
Thank you for contacting us at Amazon.com.  We have received your
e-mail inquiry and will respond to it as quickly as possible.

In the meantime, if you have questions about a recent order, you can
visit "Your Account" by clicking the link at the top of our web site,
or by accessing this URL:

http://www.amazon.com/your-account/

Once there, you can cancel or combine items from orders that have not
yet entered the shipping process, as well as change the shipping
address, payment method, or shipping method of most pending orders.

If you have questions that do not pertain to an order or account,
please visit our online Help pages; you may find the answers to many
of your questions here:

http://www.amazon.com/help/

You don't need to reply to this e-mail, as we will be able to use your
original message to answer your question.  We look forward to reading
your message and will respond as quickly as possible!


